<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Darklock — Advanced Discord Security & Protection</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Protect your Discord server with enterprise-level security. Real-time threat detection, automated moderation, and comprehensive analytics.">
