                <p class="site-hero-sub">
                    Enterprise-grade protection for your Discord community. Anti-raid, anti-nuke, smart verification, real-time threat detection, and advanced analytics — all in one bot.
                </p>
                <div class="site-hero-actions">
                    <a href="#" class="site-btn site-btn-primary" id="heroInvite">
                        <i class="fab fa-discord"></i> Add to Server
                    </a>
                    <a href="https://admin.darklock.net/dashboard" class="site-btn site-btn-ghost">
                        <i class="fas fa-external-link"></i> Open Dashboard
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="site-hero-stats">
