            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d1">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);color:#ef4444"><i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i></div>
                <h3>Anti-Raid Protection</h3>
                <p>Automatically detects and neutralizes mass-join raids, bot attacks, and coordinated spam floods in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d2">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(245,158,11,0.08);color:#f59e0b"><i class="fas fa-filter"></i></div>
                <h3>Anti-Spam Engine</h3>
                <p>Smart pattern recognition identifies and removes spam, repeated messages, invite flooding, and mention abuse.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d3">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(6,182,212,0.08);color:#06b6d4"><i class="fas fa-link-slash"></i></div>
                <h3>Anti-Phishing</h3>
                <p>Blocks malicious links, phishing attempts, and scam URLs before users can click them. Updated in real time.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d1">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(99,102,241,0.08);color:#818cf8"><i class="fas fa-chart-mixed"></i></div>
                <h3>Smart Analytics</h3>
                <p>Detailed insights into server activity, member growth, threat patterns, and moderation statistics.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d2">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(139,92,246,0.08);color:#a78bfa"><i class="fas fa-gavel"></i></div>
                <h3>Auto-Moderation</h3>
                <p>Configurable rule engine for automatic warnings, mutes, kicks, and bans. Fair, consistent, and transparent.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="site-feat-card site-reveal site-reveal-d3">
                <div class="site-feat-icon" style="background:rgba(34,197,94,0.08);color:#22c55e"><i class="fas fa-scroll"></i></div>
                <h3>Audit Logging</h3>
                <p>Full audit trail of every moderation action, config change, and security event. Exportable and searchable.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

