                <div class="site-security-checks">
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> End-to-end encrypted configuration</div>
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Zero data collection — your server stays private</div>
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> HMAC-signed file integrity protection</div>
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Role-based access control on all dashboards</div>
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Real-time threat database updates</div>
                    <div class="site-check"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> Self-hosted infrastructure — no third-party dependencies</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="site-security-visual">
                <div class="site-sec-card">
